Parrot bot is a program that runs from the command line. It automatically follows people who follow its account. If you send a direct message to the parrot bot account, it will re-tweet them automatically.

Requirements:

Runs from the command line
Automatically follows people who follow this account
Automatically re-tweet direct messages
Read Twitter account credentials from a configuration file

Usage: parrot [options]
   -p, --parrot                     Re-tweet direct messages
   -f, --follow                     Automatically follow users who are following me
   -v, --version                    Show version
   -h, --help                       Show this message
